10... a6 11. Nd5 b5 12. axb5 Rxb5
{ A move that completely changes the evaluation of the position. There is only one game played by unknown players, and the reason is that Black always automatically takes with the pawn.   12...axb5  − in the course we will demonstrate that the activity we get with this move helps us to put White in trouble and prevent the first player to achieve a comfortable position. }
