Nf3 { A nice retreat, attacking the e5-pawn. } 17... Qc7
{ Despite the bishop pair our position is still delicate because of the weak squares in our camp, so we must play with precision. }
18. Ng5
{ Taking advantage of the fact that the g5-square is weak to bring a good knight there. }
18... O-O { Safeguarding the king. Black is fine. } *

