18. Nd5 { White insists on the same theme because of the weakness on e7. }
18... Nxd5 19. exd5 O-O { The king must run away from the center. } 20. Rxe7
Rfe8 21. Rxe8+ Bxe8 22. Qe4 { Not allowing Black to take on d5. } 22... Bd7
{ However, the arrival of the rook to e8 won't allow White much choice. } *

