19... Qb6+ 20. Kh1 Nd7 21. Rxf4 f6
{ The best defense, forcing some simplifications. } 22. exf6
{ Now  22.Rh4  leads nowhere due to  22...Rf7  . } 22... Rxf6 23. Rxf6 Qxf6
{ Black is fine. } *

