22... Rac8 { With the idea of ...Qc5. } 23. Rbc1 Rf8
{ A rare but necessary move to improve our position. The idea is to play ...f6, taking advantage that the knight is pinned. }
24. Qa1 { Removing the queen from the pin. } 24... Qd8
{ Aiming at the g5-square, where our queen will be very comfortable, as it will coordinate with an eventual h-pawn push and, after ...f6, with the knight's arrival to f5. }
