11. e5 Ng4
{ Almost every time that we're allowed to play this move, it will be our favorite jump! }
12. Bxg4 Bxg4 13. f4 f6
{ With the bishop pair and the fact that the center is about to open up, our position can be defined by only one word: GOOD. }
14. Bd4 Qa5
{ Supporting the c5-pawn. White already has to be careful to avoid being worse. }
