{ We are attacking the e5-pawn practically with every piece. To keep the initiative, White should give up their light-squared bishop for the c6-knight. }
16. Bxc6 Qxc6 17. Nd5 Kh8 { Sacrificing the pawn on e7! } 18. Nxe7 Qe6
{ Black has the initiative again. The e5-pawn will fall and we are better coordinated. }
