17... Qc6 18. Nxd6 Nxe4 { Sacrificing the exchange! } 19. Nxc8 Rxc8
{ At the moment we don't even have a pawn for the exchange, but we are going to trade on g3 soon and the pawn on b2 is a strong candidate to fall.   Having the bishop pair and a pawn in an open middlegame guarantees at least nice compensation for the exchange. Let's see a possible continuation. }
20. Nc3 Qb6+ 21. Kh1 Nxg3+ 22. hxg3 Qxb2
{ Is there anyone in the room who prefers White's position? } *

