18. Rfd1
{ The normal -but sterile- continuation because taking on d5 will bring more tears than joy. }
18... Qb6 { Counterattacking b2. } 19. b4
{ 19.Qxd6  loses material because the queen is trapped after  19...Rd8  20.Qa3  Ra5! }
