17. Nc1 { Intending to remove the c5-knight with Nd3. } 17... a5
{ We continue pushing on the queenside. } 18. Nd3 Bg4
{ Good resource. If  19.f3  we go back again with  19...Bd7  and White's position has been weakened. }
19. Qxg4 Nxd3 20. Qe2 Nc5
{ We continue putting pressure on b3 and, at the same time, we can consider ideas like ...Ne6-d4, with a good position for Black. }
