{ In this early h3 line, White loses a bit of time, and hasn't supported the center with the usual f3. How can we take advantage of this? }
9... Nxe4 { The famous central fork theme. } 10. Bxf7+
{ 10.Nxe4  d5  11.Nxc6  bxc6  12.Bd3  dxe4  13.Bxe4  is a pretty simple equality.  13...Ba6  Black actually has more chances here. }
10... Kxf7 11. Nxc6 bxc6 12. Nxe4 d5 13. Nc5 Bxb2
{ White is a pawn down with not enough compensation. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
