[SetUp "1"]

{ f4 has just been played. What is Black's best continuation? } 14... Bxf4
{ Yep! Another version of the central fork theme! } 15. Rxf4 e5 16. Rf2 exd4
17. Rxd4 Ne5
{ Black has a juicy outpost on e5 for the knight and plenty of prospects with half-open files for our rooks. We have equalized comfortably. }
*

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
