{ White has made natural, but ineffective moves in the center. Can you demonstrate what happens if we're left to our own devices? }
14... Nxe4
{ This central sacrifice is totally justified given the activity of all our pieces towards the white king. Next, we will take on c3 and a2, and there's nothing White can do about it. }
15. fxe4 { 15.Nxe4  fails to  15...Qxa2+  16.Kc1  Qa1  . } 15... Bxc3 16. bxc3
Qxa2+ 17. Kc1 Qa1# { With a quick checkmate. } *

