[SetUp "1"]

{ Can you find the surprising tactical shot in this position, right out of the opening? }
13... Nxe4
{ White's position begins to fall apart all because c2 isn't sufficiently defended, and White's king hasn't moved to b1 yet. }
14. Nxe4 Nxd4 15. Bxd4 Bxd4
{ White could not capture the bishop because of mate on c2, and eventually lost the game. }
