[SetUp "1"]

{ White's king is a bit more exposed on the queenside than normal. How did White make use of this fact? }
22... Rxe3
{ Deflecting the queen from the b1-h7 diagonal so his own queen could find the light squares. }
23. Qxe3 Qf5+ 24. Qe4 { 24.Rd3  Qf6  is hopeless for White as well. } 24... Qf6
25. Rd4 Qxd4 { White has emerged up a piece and won quickly. } *

[Event "?"]
