[SetUp "1"]

22. Qc1 { What is Simon's best move? } 22... Bxg4
{ Booooom! Once again, destroying White's pawn chain, allowing his pieces to flood in towards the king. }
23. fxg4 Nxe4 24. Nfe2 { 24.Nxe4  fails to  24...Rxa2+  25.Kxa2  Qa6 } 24...
Qb4 25. hxg6 fxg6 26. Rf1 Qa5
{ The best way to maintain the pressure and create and overwhelming attack on the focal square - a2. }
27. a3 Nxc3 { Next Simon would crash through on a3, with mate coming shortly. }
*

