13. Bd3 { How did Simon create a dangerous initiative? } 13... Rxc3
{ The standard exchange sac on c3! White's king now has less cover, and Black can immediately start targetting the newly created weaknesses. }
14. bxc3 Qc7 15. Ne2 Nb6
{ Swinging the knight around, looking at the weak light squares. White will be hard-pressed to survive. }
